lement Group</b><small>Digital Solutions</small></span>\n    </a>\n    <div class=\"nav-links\">\n      <a href=\"/servicos\">Serviços</a>\n      <a href=\"/portfolio\">Portfolio</a>\n      <a href=\"/sobre\">Sobre</a>\n      <a href=\"#faq\">FAQ</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"nav-cta\">\n      <a class=\"btn-ghost\" href=\"/contacto\">Contacto</a>\n      <a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/contacto\">Pedir Orçamento</a>\n      <button class=\"menu-btn\" id=\"home-menu-btn\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Abrir menu\" aria-controls=\"home-mobile-menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n        <svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><line x1=\"4\" y1=\"8\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"8\"/><line x1=\"4\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"16\"/></svg>\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"home-mobile-menu\" id=\"home-mobile-menu\" hidden>\n  <a href=\"/servicos\">Serviços</a>\n  <a href=\"/portfolio\">Portfolio</a>\n  <a href=\"/sobre\">Sobre</a>\n  <a href=\"#faq\">FAQ</a>\n  <div class=\"home-mobile-menu-cta\">\n    <a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/contacto\">Pedir orçamento grátis</a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- ========= HERO ========= -->\n<header class=\"hero\">\n  <div class=\"planet\"></div>\n  <div class=\"glow-band\"></div>\n  <div class=\"grid-floor\"></div>\n\n  <div class=\"pill\">\n    <span class=\"pill-text\">Soluções digitais que <em style=\"font-style:italic;font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;color:#c5b6ff\">transformam</em> negócios em Portugal</span>\n    <span class=\"arrow\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7\"/></svg></span>\n  </div>\n\n  <h1 class=\"hero-title\">Websites &amp; <em>Marketing</em><br>que dão Resultados</h1>\n  <p class=\"hero-sub\">Criamos websites profissionais, lojas online e estratégias digitais para negócios portugueses. Tecnologia moderna, qualidade premium, preço justo.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"cta-row\">\n    <a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/contacto\">Começar Projeto\n      <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7\"/></svg>\n    </a>\n    <span class=\"spots\"><span class=\"dot\"></span> Disponíveis para 3 novos projetos este mês</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Portfolio cards -->\n  <div class=\"hero-portfolio\">\n    <div class=\"hp-track\">\n\n    <div class=\"proj\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open('https://apiariosterrasdapulga.pt','_blank','noopener,noreferrer')\">\n        <div class=\"preview\">\n          <span class=\"live\">Ver Live <svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></span>\n          <img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/hero-images/apiarios-terras-website.webp\" alt=\"Apiários Terras da Pulga\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover\"/>\n          <div class=\"badge\"><b style=\"color:#c0a8ff\">100</b><small>PageSpeed</small></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info\">\n          <div class=\"cat\">E-commerce · Artesanal</div>\n          <h4>Apiários Terras da Pulga</h4>\n          <p>Loja online para venda de mel e produtos apícolas com checkout MBWay e Multibanco.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">E-commerce</span><span class=\"tag\">MBWay</span><span class=\"tag\">SEO</span></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"proj\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open('https://mariamendesmassagens.pt/','_blank','noopener,noreferrer')\">\n        <div class=\"preview\">\n          <span class=\"live\">Ver Live <svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></span>\n          <img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/hero-images/maria-mendes-massagens-website.webp\" alt=\"Maria Mendes Massagens\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover\"/>\n          <div class=\"badge\"><b style=\"color:#fdba74\">Top 3</b><small>Google Local</small></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info\">\n          <div class=\"cat\">Saúde &amp; Bem-Estar</div>\n          <h4>Maria Mendes Massagens</h4>\n          <p>Website com sistema de marcações online para centro de massagens terapêuticas.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Marcações</span><span class=\"tag\">SEO Local</span><span class=\"tag\">WhatsApp</span></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"proj\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open('https://adsaoromao.pt','_blank','noopener,noreferrer')\">\n        <div class=\"preview\">\n          <span class=\"live\">Ver Live <svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></span>\n          <img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/hero-images/adsr-web-site.webp\" alt=\"AD São Romão\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover\"/>\n          <div class=\"badge\"><b style=\"color:#7dd3fc\">14 dias</b><small>Tempo de entrega</small></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info\">\n          <div class=\"cat\">Desporto · Institucional</div>\n          <h4>AD São Romão</h4>\n          <p>Website institucional para associação desportiva local com calendário de jogos e notícias.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Website</span><span class=\"tag\">Notícias</span><span class=\"tag\">Calendário</span></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"proj\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open('https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61573358033960','_blank','noopener,noreferrer')\">\n        <div class=\"preview\">\n          <span class=\"live\">Ver Live <svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></span>\n          <img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/hero-images/estrela-detail-wasg.design.webp\n\n\" alt=\"Estrela Detail &amp; Wash\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover\"/>\n          <div class=\"badge\"><b style=\"color:#fca5a5\">100%</b><small>Satisfação</small></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info\">\n          <div class=\"cat\">Automóvel · Serviços</div>\n          <h4>Estrela Detail &amp; Wash</h4>\n          <p>Website profissional para serviço de detailing e lavagem automóvel com marcações online.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Website</span><span class=\"tag\">Marcações</span><span class=\"tag\">Local</span></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"proj\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open('https://www.footballnationstore.pt','_blank','noopener,noreferrer')\">\n        <div class=\"preview\">\n          <span class=\"live\">Ver Live <svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></span>\n          <img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/hero-images/football-nation-store-design.webp\" alt=\"Football Nation Store\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover\"/>\n          <div class=\"badge\"><b style=\"color:#c0a8ff\">100%</b><small>Satisfação</small></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info\">\n          <div class=\"cat\">Design Gráfico</div>\n          <h4>Football Nation Store</h4>\n          <p>Logótipo e cartão de visita profissional para e-commerce de camisolas de clubes.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Branding</span><span class=\"tag\">Print</span><span class=\"tag\">Identidade</span></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"proj\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open('https://www.footballnationstore.pt','_blank','noopener,noreferrer')\">\n        <div class=\"preview\">\n          <span class=\"live\">Ver Live <svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></span>\n          <img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/hero-images/football-nation-store-project.webp\n\n\" alt=\"Football Nation Store\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover\"/>\n          <div class=\"badge\"><b style=\"color:#86efac\">95+</b><small>PageSpeed</small></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info\">\n          <div class=\"cat\">E-commerce · Desporto</div>\n          <h4>Football Nation Store</h4>\n          <p>Loja online completa para venda de camisolas de futebol com catálogo, pagamentos e SEO.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Loja Online</span><span class=\"tag\">Stock</span><span class=\"tag\">SEO</span></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"proj\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open('https://matiasnature.com\n','_blank','noopener,noreferrer')\">\n        <div class=\"preview\">\n          <span class=\"live\">Ver Live <svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></span>\n          <img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/hero-images/matias-nature-website.webp\" alt=\"Matias Nature - Serra da Estrela\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover\"/>\n          <div class=\"badge\"><b style=\"color:#c0a8ff\">Top 3 </b><small>Google Local</small></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info\">\n          <div class=\"cat\">Alojamento Local</div>\n          <h4>Matias Nature - Serra da Estrela</h4>\n          <p>Website para alojamento local com sistema de reservas.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Marcações</span><span class=\"tag\">SEO Local</span><span class=\"tag\">WhatsApp</span></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div><!-- /.hp-track -->\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<!-- ========= CLIENTES (rating + marquee) ========= -->\n<section id=\"clientes\" style=\"padding:80px 20px\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"rating-block reveal\">\n      <div class=\"stars-row\" aria-label=\"Avaliação 5 de 5\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.95 6.16L21.5 9.3l-4.75 4.63L17.9 20.5 12 17.27 6.1 20.5l1.15-6.57L2.5 9.3l6.55-1.14L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.95 6.16L21.5 9.3l-4.75 4.63L17.9 20.5 12 17.27 6.1 20.5l1.15-6.57L2.5 9.3l6.55-1.14L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.95 6.16L21.5 9.3l-4.75 4.63L17.9 20.5 12 17.27 6.1 20.5l1.15-6.57L2.5 9.3l6.55-1.14L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.95 6.16L21.5 9.3l-4.75 4.63L17.9 20.5 12 17.27 6.1 20.5l1.15-6.57L2.5 9.3l6.55-1.14L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.95 6.16L21.5 9.3l-4.75 4.63L17.9 20.5 12 17.27 6.1 20.5l1.15-6.57L2.5 9.3l6.55-1.14L12 2z\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"rating-text\">5/5 · Negócios que confiaram em nós</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"marquee reveal\">\n      <div class=\"marquee-track\">\n        <!-- ciclo 1 -->\n        <div class=\"m-logo\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/matias-nature-logo.png\n\n\" alt=\"Matias Nature\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Matias Nature</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/apiarios-logo.png\" alt=\"Apiários Terras da Pulga\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Apiários Terras da Pulga</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/\nmaria-mendes-logo.png\" alt=\"Maria Mendes Massagens\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Maria Mendes Massagens</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/adsr-logo.png\" alt=\"AD São Romão\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>AD São Romão</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/estrela-detail-wash-logo.png\" alt=\"Estrela Detail &amp; Wash\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Estrela Detail &amp; Wash</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/football-nation-logo.png\" alt=\"Football Nation Store\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Football Nation Store</span></div>\n        <!-- ciclo 2 (duplicado para loop infinito) -->\n        <div class=\"m-logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/matias-nature-logo.png\n\n\" alt=\"Matias Nature\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Matias Nature</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/apiarios-logo.png\" alt=\"Apiários Terras da Pulga\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Apiários Terras da Pulga</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/\nmaria-mendes-logo.png\" alt=\"Maria Mendes Massagens\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Maria Mendes Massagens</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/adsr-logo.png\" alt=\"AD São Romão\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>AD São Romão</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/estrela-detail-wash-logo.png\" alt=\"Estrela Detail &amp; Wash\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Estrela Detail &amp; Wash</span></div>\n        <div class=\"m-logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"g-mark g-mark-img\"><img src=\"https://ctflpbjvsepkbfjpgkuh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/client-logos/football-nation-logo.png\" alt=\"Football Nation Store\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></span><span>Football Nation Store</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========= WHY US ========= -->\n<section id=\"why\">\n  <div class=\"section-atmos\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rings\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>\n    <div class=\"section-sparkles\">\n      <span style=\"left:18%;top:80px;animation-delay:.2s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:24%;top:160px;animation-delay:1.4s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:32%;top:50px;animation-delay:2.6s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:40%;top:120px;animation-delay:.9s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:48%;top:200px;animation-delay:3.1s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:56%;top:60px;animation-delay:1.7s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:64%;top:170px;animation-delay:2.2s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:72%;top:90px;animation-delay:.5s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:80%;top:140px;animation-delay:2.9s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:86%;top:210px;animation-delay:1.1s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:14%;top:230px;animation-delay:3.4s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:50%;top:280px;animation-delay:.7s\"></span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section-head reveal\">\n      <span class=\"eyebrow\">Porquê nós</span>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">O que nos <em>distingue</em> da concorrência</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-sub\">Combinamos tecnologia moderna com qualidade premium e atenção ao detalhe — sem custar uma fortuna.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"features\">\n      <div class=\"feature reveal\">\n        <div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.39 4.84L20 8l-4 3.9.94 5.46L12 14.77 7.06 17.36 8 11.9 4 8l5.61-1.16L12 2z\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Design à medida</h3>\n        <p>Websites únicos, criados de raiz para refletir a identidade do teu negócio.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature reveal\">\n        <div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\"><path d=\"M13 2L3 14h7l-1 8 10-12h-7l1-8z\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Performance 95+</h3>\n        <p>PageSpeed otimizado para garantir velocidade e excelente experiência em todos os dispositivos.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature reveal\">\n        <div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\"/><path d=\"M21 21l-4.3-4.3\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>SEO Local Top 3</h3>\n        <p>Estratégia de SEO desenhada para te colocar no topo do Google Maps e da pesquisa local.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature reveal\">\n        <div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"4\" width=\"18\" height=\"14\" rx=\"2\"/><path d=\"M8 20h8M12 18v2\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>100% Responsivo</h3>\n        <p>Experiência impecável em telemóvel, tablet e desktop — onde quer que o teu cliente esteja.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature reveal\">\n        <div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\"><path d=\"M21 15a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H8l-5 3V6a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h10a4 4 0 0 1 4 4z\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Comunicação direta</h3>\n        <p>Falamos contigo em todas as fases do projeto, sem intermediários e sem rodeios.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature reveal\">\n        <div class=\"icon\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\"><path d=\"M12 8v4l3 2\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/></svg></div>\n        <h3>Entrega rápida</h3>\n        <p>Da ideia ao site online em poucas semanas — sem comprometer a qualidade.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========= SOBRE NÓS ========= -->\n<section id=\"sobre\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"about-grid\">\n      <div class=\"about-photo reveal\">\n        <div class=\"ap-stack\">\n          <div class=\"ap-glow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n          <figure class=\"ap-card ap-card-back\">\n            <img src=\"/team/mafalda.jpg\" alt=\"Mafalda Garcia — Marketing &amp; Social Media da Element\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" />\n            <figcaption>\n              <b>Mafalda Garcia</b>\n              <small>Marketing &amp; Social</small>\n            </figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <figure class=\"ap-card ap-card-front\">\n            <img src=\"/team/ricardo.jpg\" alt=\"Ricardo Jorge — CEO &amp; Co-Fundador da Element\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" />\n            <figcaption>\n              <b>Ricardo Jorge</b>\n              <small>CEO · Design &amp; Dev</small>\n            </figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"ap-badge\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <span class=\"ap-badge-dot\"></span>\n            <span class=\"ap-badge-text\">\n              <strong>Fundada em Portugal</strong>\n              <em>desde 2024</em>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ap-flag\">🇵🇹</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"about-text reveal\">\n        <span class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"align-self:flex-start\">Sobre Nós</span>\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\" style=\"text-align:left\">Conhece quem somos e a nossa <em>missão</em></h2>\n        <p class=\"about-lead\">Somos uma equipa apaixonada de profissionais criativos dedicada a criar soluções de web design excepcionais. A nossa missão é capacitar negócios em Portugal com websites inovadores que cativam <em>e</em> geram resultados reais.</p>\n        <div class=\"about-cta\">\n          <a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/contacto\">Contactar <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></a>\n          <a class=\"btn-ghost\" href=\"#trabalhos\">Ver Projetos <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\"><path d=\"M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8\"/></svg></a>\n        </div>\n        <ul class=\"about-pills\" aria-label=\"Pontos fortes da equipa\">\n          <li>\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M13 2L3 14h7l-1 8 10-12h-7l1-8z\"/></svg>\n            Resposta em 24h\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg>\n            Design · Dev · Marketing\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><path d=\"M2 12h20M12 2a15 15 0 010 20M12 2a15 15 0 000 20\"/></svg>\n            100% Português\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========= SERVIÇOS ========= -->\n<section id=\"servicos\">\n  <div class=\"section-atmos\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rings\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>\n    <div class=\"section-sparkles\">\n      <span style=\"left:16%;top:90px;animation-delay:.3s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:26%;top:180px;animation-delay:1.6s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:34%;top:60px;animation-delay:2.1s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:44%;top:140px;animation-delay:.8s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:52%;top:220px;animation-delay:3.3s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:60%;top:70px;animation-delay:1.2s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:68%;top:160px;animation-delay:2.7s\"></span>\n      <span style=\"left:76%;top:100px;animation-delay:.6s\"></